# Per-project npm auth — copy to .npmrc (gitignored):
#
#   cp .npmrc.example .npmrc
#   # edit .npmrc and paste your Automation token
#
# Use an npm Automation token (not `npm login`). Keeps publish credentials
# isolated to this repo instead of ~/.npmrc.
#
//registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=npm_xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
